## Troubleshooting
1. Failed **make setup** with __PEP517 build of a dependency failed__:
    * pyenv install 3.11.9 # or higher
    * pyenv local 3.11.9
    * poetry env use 3.11
    * poetry lock --no-update
    * make setup

